Infant mortality is not an adequate summary measure of population health.

Mathers CD(1), Salomon JA, Murray CJ.

Author information:
(1)Evidence and Information for Policy, World Health Organisation, 1211 Geneva 
27, Switzerland. mathersc@who.int

Comment on
    J Epidemiol Community Health. 2003 May;57(5):344-6.

